\left(R_{2}\right)_{y}\leq\left(R_{1}\right)_{y} & \left(G_{2}\right)_{y}\geq\left(G_{1}\right)_{y} & \left(B_{2}\right)_{y}\leq\left(B_{1}\right)_{y}
